ed="T" n="0730c27"/><persName key="A009243">釋會隱</persName>，不詳何許人也。精明之氣，綽有盈<lb
ed="T" n="0730c28"/>餘，處于等夷<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g630"/>，若雞群之見鶴也。<date from-iso="+0650-02-10" key="j19585081970910" to-iso="+0684-01-25"><persName key="A002146">天皇</persName></date>朝慎<lb
ed="T" n="0730c29"/>選高學名德，<persName key="A009243">隱</persName>膺斯選。<date from-iso="+0665-01-25" key="j19639711964354" to-iso="+0666-02-12"><name>麟德</name>二年</date>勅北門<pb ed="T" n="0731a" xml:id="T50.2061.0731a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0731a01"/>西龍門修書所<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n647"/>，同與<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A009244">玄則</persName>等一十人<lb
ed="T" n="0731a02"/>於一切經中略出精義玄文三十卷，號《禪林<lb
ed="T" n="0731a03"/>要鈔》，書成奏呈，勅藏祕閣。<persName key="A009243">隱</persName>亦甞預翻譯，<lb
ed="T" n="0731a04"/><persName key="A009244">玄則</persName>頗聞著述，<persName key="A002146">高宗</persName>朝斯為龍象之最焉。</p>
